<p>I need to match an associated model on a user id, I thought the below code would work since I do get the <code>user_id</code> back for <code>ArticleUser</code>, but it's not giving me the <code>FavoriteArticle</code> I need.</p>  <p>The data comes back as <code>null</code> for the <code>FavoriteArticle</code> model, and yes, there is a <code>favorite_articles</code> table in the DB.</p>  <pre><code>public $hasOne = array(     'ArticleUser',     'FavoriteArticle' =&gt; array(         'className' =&gt; 'FavoriteArticle',         'conditions' =&gt; array(             'FavoriteArticle.user_id' =&gt; 'ArticleUser.user_id'         ),         'dependent' =&gt; true     )  ); </code></pre>